metadata.name: Cyber Warrior #1
metadata.description:
Join the warriors of CyberVersum! Cyber Warriors Army
        is a collection of 8000 avatar tokens procedurally generated with
         artwork by a pro illustrator. These ETH NFTs serves as a pass to the
         CyberVersum, which is a developing digital space for esports,
         online games, competitive events and Web3 culture.
         Visit [www.cyberwarriorsarmy.com](https://www.cyberwarriorsarmy.com/)
         to learn more.
